11. Grant option and admin option diffrence ?

=> ✅ With Grant option :

Kisi user ko 'Object Privilege' dete waqt "WITH GRANT OPTION" do — toh wo user aage doosron ko bhi wahi privilege de sakta hai!

** IF DBA REVOKE FROM 'RAMESH', RAMESH AND OTHERS PRIVILAGE GONE**

👉 Example:

DBA → Ramesh ko diya:
GRANT SELECT ON employees TO ramesh WITH GRANT OPTION;
          │
          ▼
Ramesh → Suresh ko de sakta hai:
GRANT SELECT ON employees TO suresh;


=> ✅ WITH ADMIN OPTION :

Kisi user ko 'System Privilege' dete waqt "WITH ADMIN OPTION" do — toh wo user aage doosron ko bhi wahi privilege de sakta hai!

** IF DBA REVOKE FROM 'RAMESH', RAMESH NO LONGER ACCESS BUT OTHERS CAN DO **
------------------------------------------------------------

12. What is System Privilege and Object Privilege?

=> ✅ System Privileges -- 

        👉 CREATE SESSION
        👉 CREATE TABLE
        👉 CREATE VIEW
        👉 CREATE USER
        👉 ALTER SYSTEM
