25. How to enable FLASHBACK ?

👉 Bring the Database to mount state (SHUTDOWN IMMEDIATE; -> STARTUP MOUNT;) 
👉 ALTER DATABASE FLASHBACK ON;
👉 ALTER DATABASE OPEN;
